description: The image displays the Nike logo, which features the word "NIKE" in bold, black capital letters with a swoosh design underneath.
The image shows the Amazon logo, which consists of the word "amazon" in white capital letters with a yellow smiley arrow beneath it.

A red apple with a stem is isolated on a white background.

A whole pineapple with its green top is placed on a white surface.
